 |accessdate  = 2015-03-08
 |lang        = eng
}}</ref>, «The Signal Service» (1921)<ref>{{книга
 | автор         = Priestley, Raymond Edward
 | заглавие      = The Signal Service in the European War of 1914-1918 (France)
